      "ref": "Psalm 12:5",
      "source_id": "kjv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-kjv2006/PSA012.htm",
      "text": "For the oppression of the poor, for the sighing of the needy, now will I arise, saith the LORD; I will set [him] in safety [from him that] puffeth at him.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 12:5",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA012.htm",
      "text": "Because of the oppression of the poor, because of the sighing of the needy, Now will I arise, saith Jehovah; I will set him in the safety he panteth for.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 12:5",
      "source_id": "web",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA012.htm",
      "text": "“Because of the oppression of the weak and because of the groaning of the needy, I will now arise,” says the LORD; “I will set him in safety from those who malign him.”",
